sources.title: 4K The Giant Leeches 1959 - Bloodthirsty Monster Horror! Directed by Bernard L. Kowalski
sources.description:
In Florida's wetlands, monstrous creatures lurk underwater, abducting townspeople to a hidden lair. A warden and allies uncover the horror: bloodthirsty beings feeding on captives. After a deadly confrontation and an explosive finale, one menace silently escapes.

Original title: Attack of the Giant Leeches (1959)
